channel.title: Help on new computer build
channel.description:
So, I'm building a pc off of newegg. My price range is $300-$350. This is what I came up with, but if you could find a better build for the same price, let me know. Feedback is greatly appreciated. I'm just using it for programming and browsing the internet and probably watching movies and streaming videos.
CPU: http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16819113286 MOBO: http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16813157323 GPU: http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16814131496 HD: http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16822236339 RAM: http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16820231276
